### Research Software Readiness Checker Pro v1.0.0

#### Features:
- Automated analysis of 6 research-readiness criteria
- Weighted scoring system (README:20, License:15, Tests:25, CI/CD:15, Versioning:10, Citation:15)
- PDF, HTML, and JSON export
- Persistent history tracking
- Confetti animation for high scores

#### How to use:
Download index.html and open in Chrome/Edge/Brave
